      <title>麦考尔率领美国议员在中国军演后访问台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/us-lawmakers-led-by-mccaul-visit-taiwan-after-chinese-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由美国国会议员组成的两党代表团于周日抵达台湾，这是自总统赖清德就职以来的首次访问，也是在中国结束一年来最大规模的台湾军事演习的第二天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/us-lawmakers-led-by-mccaul-visit-taiwan-after-chinese-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:39:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国《金融时报》称，美国可能取消向沙特阿拉伯出售部分武器的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/us-may-lift-ban-on-some-weapons-sales-to-saudi-arabia-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》报道，美国可能会在几周内取消向沙特阿拉伯出售进攻性武器的禁令，这是两国关系改善的进一步迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/us-may-lift-ban-on-some-weapons-sales-to-saudi-arabia-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 12:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨表示资本市场联盟是马克龙会议的优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/scholz-says-capital-markets-union-a-priority-for-macron-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨表示，建立欧洲资本市场联盟将是本周与法国总统马克龙会晤时的优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/scholz-says-capital-markets-union-a-priority-for-macron-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军队不顾法院裁决继续进入拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/war-in-gaza-israeli-military-proceeds-into-rafah-despite-world-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管国际法院以保护平民为名下令停止此类活动，但以色列军方仍在加沙南部城市拉法继续对哈马斯采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/war-in-gaza-israeli-military-proceeds-into-rafah-despite-world-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 10:13:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内战愈演愈烈之际，苏丹军队加深与俄罗斯和伊朗的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/sudan-s-army-deepens-ties-with-russia-iran-as-civil-war-rages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹军方表示，准备从俄罗斯购买武器，作为交换，俄罗斯允许其在红海沿岸建立一个军用加油站，这对美国来说是一个打击，因为美国的对手正在这个因内战而分裂的非洲国家获得影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-26/sudan-s-army-deepens-ties-with-russia-iran-as-civil-war-rages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 09:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰将年长士兵派往前线，但军队需要年轻人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-26/ukraine-sends-older-troops-to-war-with-russia-as-army-runs-short-of-men</link>
      <description><![CDATA[战争初期，祖父母争相报名。但现在该国发现，击退俄罗斯的进步将取决于动员年轻人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-05-26/ukraine-sends-older-troops-to-war-with-russia-as-army-runs-short-of-men</guid>
